snippet.title: Tetris Effect: Connected - Gameplay Preview - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Experience Tetris like you’ve never seen, heard, or felt before in the innovative Tetris Effect: Connected game. Play solo and take on your friends in online or local multiplayer! Coming to Nintendo Switch on Oct. 8!

Learn more: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/tetris-effect-connected-switch/
